Simba Wion
[[File:Baby-diaperfur tattoo.jpg|thumb|Simba Wion and StarvinDeformed Wolf show the world how HARDCORE they are.]]
'''Simba Wion''' is a totally ''hardcore'' [[babyfur]] from [[Colorado]]. He and his [[Prostitute|mate]], FagWuff, have managed to alienate themselves from other [[furry|furries]], from other [[babyfur]]s, and from [[God]] with one single epic move: getting tattoos of a piss-diapered baby lion and baby wolf on their scrawny arms. This [[fail|EPIC FAIL]] move may have hurt their ability to obtain a job, but that assumes they were employable in the first place.

==The [[Lion]] Behind the [[Tattoo|Tat]]==
Not much can be found out about Simba Wion, as he is an [[babyfur|outcast among outcasts]] -- avoided by local Colorado furs and furs throughout the tubes. However, through diligent [[google|research]], the following [[bullshit|facts]] have been discovered about Simba Wion.

* He lives in his parents' basement
* Both he and his parents' live off of [[you]]r tax money
* He has Gonosyphiherpalies
* He has trapped little boys in public bathrooms and forced them to [[watersports|pee]] on his pants
* He is unemployable, as interviewers are always heard shouting "JESUS CHRIST IT'S A PIDDLING LION, GTFO!"
* He watches you pee in the bathroom

